data.description: Back on the market at no fault of sellers!  Don't miss this rare find in Prince George County.  1.26 ACRES  This gem is tucked away in the back of Beechwood Manor on a cul-de-sac lot.  Lovely floor plan with a Great Room, Office/Study, full bath, and Utility Room on the lower level.  On the mid level you will find the Eat-in Kitchen and spacious Living Room and on the top level there are 3 spacious bedrooms and a full bath.  Lots of updates.  Newer Carpet and HVAC.  Multi level decking, elaborate landscaping, and 2 detached sheds.  Close to Williamsburg, Fort Gregg-Adams, and Jordan Point Marina.
